<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TimeML><TIMEX3 tid="t0" functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME"/>Unions representing thousands of BBC technicians  and journalists <EVENT eid="e1" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">decided</EVENT> <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DATE">Wednesday</TIMEX3> to <EVENT eid="e2" class="I_ACTION" tense="INFINITIVE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">call</EVENT> off a series of 24-hour strikes over  pay and hours, officials <EVENT eid="e3" class="REPORTING" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">said</EVENT>.&#13;
